apps.localizedDescription: A flexible, fast and open-source Minecraft Java Edition launcher for iOS.
apps.name: PojavLauncher
apps.subtitle: A flexible, fast and open-source Minecraft Java Edition launcher for iOS
apps.versionDescription:
Added in Minecraft 1.17, Deepslate makes up the foundation of a Minecraft world, just above bedrock. We chose this name because of the majority of changes in this version targeting core changes.

With this release of PojavLauncher, we refined features, fixed bugs, and implemented small additions to existing ones to buff user experience. While there are not many notable changes to discuss here, there are some we can show:

• Implemented a controller configurator
•Increased reliability in various places
• Added haptics to the on-screen controls
• Switched to new input methods to speed up control times
• Secured demo mode
• Added new preferences to control more of the app
• Resolve various issues with windowing in older versions
•and many, many more!

This is the last major release of PojavLauncher that will support iOS 12 and 13. Important security patches and bug fixes will be applied when required for a limited time, however take note that issues encountered will not be considered high priority. See more information in #547.

• YTSpeed

• Updated YouTube from "19.23.3" to "19.29.1"

• Added "Hide Home Tab" option ([@bhackel](https://github.com/bhackel)) [210]()

• Added "Disable Engagement Overlay" option ([@bhackel](https://github.com/bhackel))
• Added "Classic Seek Anywhere" gesture ([@bhackel](https://github.com/bhackel))
• Added YTHeaders submodule ([@Balackburn](https://github.com/Balackburn))

Bug Fixes

• Fixed escaping quotes issue ([@AlexInABox](https://github.com/AlexInABox)) [187]()
• Fixed SDK caching issues ([@arichornlover](https://github.com/arichornlover))
• Fixed crash caused by edge case ([@bhackel](https://github.com/bhackel))
• Fixed compilation errors ([@bhackel](https://github.com/bhackel))
• Fixed home contents bug ([@bhackel](https://github.com/bhackel))
• Fixed "Fullscreen to the Right" functionality ([@bhackel](https://github.com/bhackel))
• Fixed redefinition of •userInterfaceIdiom issue ([@asdfzxcvbn](https://github.com/asdfzxcvbn))

Improvements

• Cleaned up and added workflow settings ([@bhackel](https://github.com/bhackel))
• Updated compiling for YouTube v19.21.2+ ([@arichornloverALT](https://github.com/arichornloverALT))
• Removed deprecated and redundant code ([@bhackel](https://github.com/bhackel))
• Synchronized delete•workflow•runs.yml ([@arichornlover](https://github.com/arichornlover))

Localization

• Updated Portuguese localization ([@VictorxD70](https://github.com/VictorxD70)) [253](), [254]()
